reviews.text: A very good neighborhood restaurant with many nice local food.
Good food, fast and efficient,great staff
Food was just ok but waitresses were so hurry to collect dishes twice without asking even my son went to restroom only.
Price is suitable for the high quality food.
Neighborhood friendly price, with old classic taste you can get, environment is ok, but service need a hell lot of polishing, those waitresses are a bit not-so-friendly. Damm.

reviews.text: 很垃圾的一家餐廳，老板仔管理失敗，任由員工偷懶，客人想点餐乍帝扮睇唔到，自從裝修後換了廚師後，味道更是一跌千里。遲早關門大吉。
地點很方面，貼近長沙灣地鐵站。食物質素跟一般茶餐廳差不多。
食物還好 價錢適中 唯一的士 座位不舒服
A very good neighborhood restaurant with many nice local food.

丹麥酥居然不可以改成方包（有些跟方包的餐）。
店員居然直接的吧餐具洗滌筒放在正在吃東西的食客的桌上...🤢🤢🤢
